text: Sambuugiin Oyuuntsetseg (born 15 December 1964) is a Mongolian archer. Oyuuntsetseg competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics.Sambuugiin Oyuuntsetseg == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia
